name: SVGURIReference
description: The SVGURIReference interface is used to reflect the href attribute and the deprecated xlink:href attribute.

members.name: SVGURIReference.href
members.description: An SVGAnimatedString that represents the value of the href attribute, and, on elements that are defined to support it, the deprecated xlink:href attribute. On getting href, an SVGAnimatedString object is returned that reflects the href attribute, and if the element is defined to support the deprecated xlink:href attribute, additionally reflects that deprecated attribute.
